      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/36/12",
      "text": [
        " : \"فِيمَا قَتَلَ اَلْمِعْرَاضُ لاَ بَأْسَ بِهِ إِذَا كَانَ إِنَّمَا يُصْنَعُ لِذَلِكَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4132 - Zurara heard Abu Ja'far Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as), saying:\n\"There is no harm in what the 'mi'raad' (a hunting tool) kills, as long as it is specifically made for that purpose.\""
        ]
      }
